MG_RUN_FETBOY_RUN ----------------------------- The aim of this map is for the Terrorists to run around 4 stages of the map trying to dodge the smash blocks that fly out of the cannons which 4 CT's control! The stages get more difficult as time goes on, if the T's do manage to make it to the end of the map then they will be able to kill the CT's unless they got shot over the top by the cannons ^^. Each stage has a time limit on to make it to the end: *STAGE 1* = 1 Minute *STAGE 2* = 50 Seconds *STAGE 3* = 1 Minute *STAGE 4* = Unlimited Time. Map Requires mp_limitteams 0 server setting. *IMPORTANT NOTE ABOUT PLAYER SLOTS* This map is 20 slots so that there is an even amount of T's on each side. If you would like a map with 32+ slots then send me a FPSB private message and I will send you it. You can find my prefab cannon here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/prefabs/3354 Thanks Paul_Deagle (aka [SG] Paul)
